title: TREBARTHA OAK
Description: A timeless farmhouse style dining table, our Trebartha range is classic and contemporary but with a creative flair. An angular base, hand-crafted from oak(80mm thick), is married with our traditional English and french oak top, making this an all-oak table. The perfect table to take you from every-day home life and weekend breakfasts to stylish dinner parties and special occasions.
